    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Clathria unoriginalis. Field photos of holotype (A) and IZC00048439 (B). Cross sections showing choanosomal skeleton (C) and ectosomal skeleton (D). E: Thick style. F: Head of thin style and side view of chela. G: Chelae. C–G from holotype." ;
